{CritterProperty::IsTraitFastMetabolism}{Name}{Fast Metabolism}
{CritterProperty::IsTraitFastMetabolism}{Desc}{Your metabolic rate is twice normal.  This means that you are much less resistant to radiation and poison, but your body heals faster.}
{CritterProperty::IsTraitFastMetabolism}{Pic}{art\skilldex\FASTMETA.FRM}
{CritterProperty::IsTraitBruiser}{Name}{Bruiser}
{CritterProperty::IsTraitBruiser}{Desc}{A little slower, but a little bigger.  You may not hit as often, but they will feel it when you do!  Your total action points are lowered, but your Strength is increased.}
{CritterProperty::IsTraitBruiser}{Pic}{art\skilldex\BRUISER.FRM}
{CritterProperty::IsTraitSmallFrame}{Name}{Small Frame}
