{CritterProperty::IsTraitKamikaze}{Pic}{art\skilldex\KAMIKAZE.FRM}
{CritterProperty::IsTraitHeavyHanded}{Name}{Heavy Handed}
{CritterProperty::IsTraitHeavyHanded}{Desc}{You swing harder, not better.  Your attacks are very brutal, but lack finesse.  You rarely cause a good critical, but you always do more melee damage.}
{CritterProperty::IsTraitHeavyHanded}{Pic}{art\skilldex\HEAVYHND.FRM}
{CritterProperty::IsTraitFastShot}{Name}{Fast Shot}
{CritterProperty::IsTraitFastShot}{Desc}{You don't have time to aim for a targeted attack, because you attack faster than normal people.  It costs you one less action point for guns and thrown weapons.}
