{CritterProperty::IsTraitGoodNatured}{Name}{Good Natured}
{CritterProperty::IsTraitGoodNatured}{Desc}{You studied less-combative skills as you were growing up.  Your combat skills start at a lower level, but First Aid, Doctor, Speech and Barter are substantially improved.}
