{2000000000}{}{
Hot keys:

F1 - Help on/off.
F2 - Save messages in a file.
F3 - Save a screenshot.
F4 - Text input panels toggle.
F5 - Expanded message window toggle.
F6 - Player names display toggle.
F8 - Mouse scrolling toggle (helps in window mode).
F12 - Minimize client window.
Arrow keys - Map scrolling.
Esc - Menu.
Pause/Break - Automatic language switching in command line.
<,> - Turn counter-clockwise/clockwise.
Home - Center on character (works on the global map).
A - Attack.
C - Character sheet.
G - Pick an item from the ground.
I - Inventory.
P - Pipboy.
F - Fixboy.
B - Switch active slots.
M - Switch mouse menu.
N - Switch item mode.
S - Skilldex.
Z - Map zooming.
1-8 - Fast skill choose.
? - Current game time.
+,- - Brightness adjust.
Ctrl + +,- - Sound volume adjust.
Shift + +,- - Music volume adjust.
Alt + +,- - Sleep adjust.

Communication shortcuts:
Type . or /, then:
s S - shout,
w W - whisper,
e E - emotion,
r R - radio.
Placing space character after command is not needed and ignored if present.
Type a message and press Enter.

Also message sending is available with:
Ctrl + Enter - shout,
Alt + Enter - wisper,
Shift + Enter - radio.
}

